Feel-in
(Rick Dougherty)

Feel in
I got a little feel in
When she wasn't lookin'
A feel-in of love

Teardrops
Rolling down on my face
She kicked me in my place
My feeling of love

Feel it
All my life I'll feel it
I wish I never met you, girl
I'll never come again

Feelin's WHOAAAAA
Feelin's
Feelin's
Again (falsetto) of love!
